{"attribution":"Federal Trade Commission, Scams and Your Small Business, Simplified Chinese, July 2023; no FTC endorsement or affiliation is implied.","cases":[{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-001","input":"当诈骗犯将黑手伸向你的企业或非营利组织时，会对你的声誉和盈亏带来损害。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-001","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-002","input":"那么，有哪些最佳的保护措施呢？","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-002","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-003","input":"现在，让我们来了解下当企业成为诈骗目标时会有哪些迹象。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-003","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-004","input":"然后，告诉你的员工和同事有哪些相关的注意事项，以防被骗。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-004","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-005","input":"诈骗犯会伪装成你信任的某个人。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-005","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-006","input":"他们会假称是你知道的某个公司或政府机构，让你向他们付款。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-006","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-007","input":"但是，这是一个骗局。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-007","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-008","input":"诈骗犯会营造一种紧迫感，甚至施以威胁，以引起你的恐慌。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-008","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-009","input":"他们会希望你立即行动，不给你机会进行查证。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-009","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-010","input":"切勿因任何人的催促而急于向其付款或透露敏感的商业信息。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-010","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-011","input":"诈骗犯会要求你以特定方式进行付款。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-011","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-012","input":"他们通常会要求你通过电汇，加密货币或礼品卡的方式汇款。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-012","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-013","input":"切勿向要求你使用上述支付方法的人员付款。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-013","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-014","input":"最有效的防御就是训练有素的员工。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-014","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-015","input":"对员工进行培训，告诉他们不要通过电子邮件发送密码或敏感信息，即使索要这些信息的邮件看似来自某位经理。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-015","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-016","input":"向员工介绍常见的诈骗方法，并鼓励他们在发现疑似诈骗行为时与同事进行讨论。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-016","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-017","input":"确保采购和发票的审批流程清晰明确，并要求你的员工仔细核查所有的发票。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-017","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-018","input":"留意对方要求的付款方式，并让你的员工也多加关注。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-018","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-019","input":"如果对方要求你通过电汇，加密货币或礼品卡的方式支付，切勿付款。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-019","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-020","input":"诈骗犯往往会伪造他们的电话号码，因此，请勿相信来电显示。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-020","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-021","input":"如果你收到别人主动发来的短信或电子邮件，请勿点击其中的任何链接，打开附件或是下载其中的文件。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-021","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-022","input":"诈骗犯会通过这种方式将恶意软件加载到你的网络上，或是试图说服你汇款或透露敏感信息。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-022","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-023","input":"诈骗犯有时甚至还会黑入你所认识的某个人的社交媒体账号，向你发送一些看似真实但其实是虚假的信息。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-023","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-024","input":"在和新的公司开展业务之前，请在网上输入该公司的名称外加“诈骗”或“投诉”字样进行搜索。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-024","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-025","input":"了解他人对该公司的评价。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-025","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-026","input":"向你信任的人士寻求建议。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-026","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-027","input":"诈骗犯会伪造虚假发票，使其看起来像是你为自己的企业订购过某些产品或服务。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-027","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-028","input":"他们的目的是要让为你支付账单的人员认定这些发票的真实性，从而支付款项。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-028","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-029","input":"但，这一切都是假的。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-029","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-030","input":"或者，诈骗犯可能会打电话声称想要“确认”某个既有订单，“核实”地址，或是提供“免费”的产品目录或样品。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-030","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-031","input":"如果你答应了上述要求，那么就会收到你其实并未订购的商品，而之后，对方就会迫使你付款。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-031","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-032","input":"这时，请千万不要付款。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-032","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-033","input":"请记住，如果你收到了并未订购的商品，那么你有合法权利将其保留并免费使用。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-033","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-034","input":"诈骗犯会试图诓骗你为根本不存在的广告或被列入某个虚假的企业名录付款。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-034","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-035","input":"他们会要求你透露你的联系信息以便“免费”将你列入名录，或宣称打来电话只是为了“确认”你的信息。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-035","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-036","input":"之后，你会收到大额账单，这时诈骗犯会利用他们先前在电话中了解到的详细信息——甚至是录音——迫使你付款。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-036","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-037","input":"诈骗犯会假装成你认识或信任的某个人，试图恐吓你或催促你汇款或透露信息。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-037","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-038","input":"例如：诈骗犯声称他们来自某个公用事业公司，由于你拖欠账单（实为虚构）即将暂停你的用气，用电或用水服务。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-038","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-039","input":"诈骗犯声称他们来自某个政府机构，威胁要吊销你的营业执照，罚款甚至是起诉你。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-039","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-040","input":"他们可能会声称原因是你有拖欠税费或需要更新执照或登记信息。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-040","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-041","input":"一些诈骗犯会说服你购买工作场所合规海报，而这可以通过美国劳工部免费获取。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-041","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-042","input":"一些诈骗犯会诓骗你为申请政府的所谓企业援助计划付款，而这从头到尾就是场骗局。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-042","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-043","input":"诈骗犯伪装成美国专利商标局的工作人员，威胁你如果不立即支付某项费用就会失去商标专用权。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-043","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-044","input":"其他一些情况下，他们会假称你欠下了其他注册服务的费用。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-044","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-045","input":"一些诈骗犯会宣称他们来自某个科技公司，威胁你如果不立即汇款就会失去企业网站的 URL。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-045","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-046","input":"技术支持型诈骗会在一开始给你打电话，或在你的页面上弹出警示信息。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-046","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-047","input":"诈骗犯会假装是来自某个知名的技术公司，声称你的电脑存在安全问题。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-047","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-048","input":"他们的目的其实只是为了骗取你的钱财，访问你的电脑，或两者皆有。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-048","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-049","input":"他们会要求你就修复某个你根本不存在的问题，将你的企业纳入根本不存在的或毫无用处的电脑维护项目付款，或潜入你的电脑网络抓取机密数据来实施身份盗窃。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-049","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-050","input":"网络诈骗犯会诓骗员工向其汇款，或透露诸如密码或银行信息等保密或敏感信息。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-050","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-051","input":"其通常会在一开始以网络钓鱼电子邮件，社交媒体联系人或看似来自某个可靠来源的电话（如主管或其他高层人员）——来制造紧迫感或引起你的害怕。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-051","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-052","input":"还有一些电子邮件可能会看起来像是常规的密码更新申请，或其他自动发送的消息，但实际上它们的目的都是要试图窃取你的信息。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-052","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-053","input":"诈骗犯还会使用恶意软件来锁住组织的文件以便勒索。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-053","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-054","input":"一些诈骗犯会兜售虚假的企业辅导计划，惯用方式是使用伪造的推荐信、视频、研讨会上的演讲以及营销电话。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-054","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-055","input":"他们会假装承诺，如果您想要企业取得成功，只要购买他们“经过验证”的独家系统，就能实现显著效果。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-055","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-056","input":"他们还会在一开始以低价来诱惑你，目的是为了在以后骗取你大量的钱财。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-056","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-057","input":"而事实上，诈骗犯并不会给这些新手企业家们任何他们想要的帮助，只会给其留下巨额债务。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-057","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-058","input":"一些诈骗犯宣称他们可以更换对你公司的产品或服务的负面评价，添加正面评价，或是提升你在评分网站上的得分。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-058","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-059","input":"但是，发布虚假评价是违法行为。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-059","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-060","input":"FTC 指南规定代言（包括评价）必须反映真实的意见和代言人的亲身体验。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-060","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-061","input":"一些诈骗犯会承诺以低价处理信用卡交易，或提供更优惠的设备租赁服务。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-061","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-062","input":"这些诈骗犯会利用小号字体的细则，半真半假的表述和彻头彻尾的谎言来骗取企业主签署合同。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-062","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-063","input":"一些毫无道德的销售代理甚至还会要求企业主签署空白文件。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-063","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-064","input":"千万不要这样做。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-064","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-065","input":"其他一些已知的骗局是事后更改条款。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-065","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-066","input":"请你要求销售人员当场提供所有文件的副本。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-066","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-067","input":"如果他们予以拒绝或承诺稍后提供以拖延时间，那么这可能就表明你遇到了诈骗。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-067","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-068","input":"一些诈骗犯会给出看似可信的理由来通过支票向你超额支付。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-068","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-069","input":"之后，他们会要求你将多出的钱款返还给他们或某个其他人员。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-069","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-070","input":"但这是张虚假支票，即便它可能在你的账户中显示“已结清”。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-070","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-071","input":"在银行发现支票有问题时，诈骗犯早已收到了你汇给他们的钱款，而你将需要负责偿还银行。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-071","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-072","input":"一些诈骗犯会以其他可疑的行为作掩护，例如，宣称可以提供高薪的零工工作，但之后却无法兑现。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-072","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-073","input":"或者，他们会试图向你兜售对你来说根本没有必要的服务，宣称你需要借此来完善你的企业信用报告。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-073","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-074","input":"另外，在遭受了自然灾害之后，一些未经授权的承包商和诈骗犯会向你许诺，他们会为你提供快速维修，清洁或垃圾清理等服务来帮助你的企业恢复运营。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-074","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-075","input":"但实际上，他们口中的这些“承诺”根本就不会兑现。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-075","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-076","input":"通知你所在州的总检察长。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-076","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-077","input":"请记住，你最有效的防御就是训练有素的员工。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-077","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-078","input":"向员工介绍常见的诈骗方式。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-078","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-079","input":"与你的员工一同阅览本手册。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-079","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-080","input":"FTC 致力于帮助小型企业主避免受骗，保护他们的计算机和网络，并保证其客户数据的安全。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-080","split":"booklet"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1/sentence-081","input":"您可以在此找到有关针对小型企业的诈骗以及如何避免这些诈骗的信息，还有关于小型企业网络安全的信息，以帮助小型企业主确保其网络安全。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://consumer.ftc.gov/system/files/consumer_ftc_gov/pdf/1033A_Scams%20and%20Your%20Small%20Business_July%202023_ZHS_508.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-081","split":"booklet"}}],"converter_output_used":false,"dataset":"blind-v2","id":"ftc-small-business-simplified-v1","input_only":true,"license":"U.S. Public Domain","modification_notice":"Extracted only complete Simplified Chinese prose sentences from the checksum-pinned FTC-authored PDF, joined PDF layout wraps, removed headings, page furniture, navigation URLs, phone instructions, and incomplete fragments, and added input-only provenance; no images, seals, expected text, or converter output were used.","purpose":"candidate_source_pilot","review_policy":"domain_and_risk_must_be_assigned_from_input_only","source_class":"public_domain","stats":{"by_split":{"booklet":81},"eligible_pending_review":81,"exclusions":{},"raw_cases":81},"upstream_revision":"FTC Scams and Your Small Business, Simplified Chinese, July 2023; PDF Last-Modified 2023-09-12T14:41:50Z; raw SHA-256: c5bdddabd3570861a623134a768d253cc3a9200db683303d09624f3736c1b6a7","version":1}
